class Solution {
    public int maxDepth(String s) {
        int open=0;
        int max=0;
        for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++){
            if(s.charAt(i)=='('){
                open++;
                if(max<open){
                    max++;
                }
            }
            else if(s.charAt(i)==')'){
                open--;
            }
        }
        return max;
    }
}
open ( then ++ ,if ) do open --
max check with open ,if open is greater than max so it will increase max++